race.comment: KING NANGAR (2) stalked the lead from a middle draw and boxed on well to finish 2.25 lengths back in third (25.70) at this track in a Mix over 450m. Makes plenty of appeal. MOST DETERMINED (7) is a progressive type who recorded his 2nd career win last time out (25.39) at this track. Winner at his latest appearance in one of the quickest times on the card. Leading chance again. NANGAR CHARM (1) was safely held on debut after settling well back when fourth (26.20) at this track over 450m. Has the inside box this time. Meets a moderate line up and should do much better. Something for the Multiples: SPEED HOLES (5)
